<li id="cite_note-7"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><a href="Cloward-Piven_strategy#cite_ref-7">↑</a></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.library.ca.gov/crb/95/notes/v3n1.pdf">The NYC government was running deficits well before the strategy was even devised</a>, so we're talking about some major <a href="https://rationalwiki.org/wiki/Time_travel" title="Time travel">time travel</a> shit here.</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-8"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><a href="Cloward-Piven_strategy#cite_ref-8">↑</a></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://quote.ucsd.edu/jskrentny/files/2014/08/S0898588X9800131Xa.pdf">Coalition-Building and the Politics of Electoral Capture During the Nixon Administration: African Americans, Labor, Latinos</a>, <i>Studies in American Political Development</i></span>
</li>
</ol></div>

